&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design, develop, and maintain scalable &lt;strong&gt;data pipelines&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;ETL/ELT workflows&lt;/strong&gt; on AWS.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modernize legacy data platforms by migrating &lt;strong&gt;Apache Airflow/MWAA&lt;/strong&gt; workloads to AWS-native orchestration services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Migrate and optimize &lt;strong&gt;Amazon EMR&lt;/strong&gt; workloads to &lt;strong&gt;AWS Glue&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and implement scalable &lt;strong&gt;data lake&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;data warehouse&lt;/strong&gt; solutions using AWS services.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop robust data models, semantic layers, and standardized KPI definitions to support business analytics.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain &lt;strong&gt;data quality&lt;/strong&gt;, validation, anomaly detection, and monitoring frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement &lt;strong&gt;metadata management&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;data lineage&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;data governance&lt;/strong&gt; best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop automated deployment pipelines and infrastructure using &lt;strong&gt;Infrastructure as Code (IaC)&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimize data pipelines for performance, scalability, reliability, and cost efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with business stakeholders to understand reporting requirements and translate them into scalable data solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support &lt;strong&gt;QuickSight&lt;/strong&gt; semantic datasets, dashboard optimization, and Power BI migration initiatives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in UAT, production deployments, knowledge transfer, and post-production support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
