&lt;h4 data-start=&quot;692&quot; data-end=&quot;713&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner directly with client business stakeholders and subject-matter experts to deeply understand workflows, including undocumented edge cases and tribal knowledge.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and facilitate discovery workshops, user shadowing sessions, and requirements gathering activities, translating findings into clear user stories, acceptance criteria, and process documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own and prioritize the product backlog in close collaboration with the client&#39;s Product Owner, balancing business value, technical dependencies, and delivery sequencing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the connective tissue between business intent and engineering execution, ensuring the distributed development team builds the right solution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Document workflows, business rules, and conditional logic with enough precision to support codification and automated testing.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support UAT planning and execution, including building structured test scenarios mapped to real business workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify opportunities to simplify, streamline, and improve existing business processes rather than simply digitizing them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain clear, proactive communication across stakeholders while surfacing risks, dependencies, and key decisions early.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
