&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will bring deep expertise in at least one primary engineering discipline while maintaining strong architectural awareness across frontend, backend, mobile, and cloud infrastructure environments. This role requires excellent communication skills, strong technical judgment, and the ability to partner closely with both engineering teams and client stakeholders.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and coordinate a distributed team of frontend, backend, mobile, and DevOps engineers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide architectural guidance across all layers of the platform&lt;/li&gt;
