&lt;li&gt;Conduct code reviews and enforce coding standards and best practices&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary technical point of contact between the delivery team and client stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify technical risks and proactively propose mitigation strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate sprint planning, standups, and retrospectives in collaboration with project management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support cross-functional collaboration across frontend, backend, mobile, and infrastructure teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
