&lt;li class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;3+ years in a technical lead, staff engineer, or architect-level role leading cross-functional teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Strong hands-on engineering experience in at least one primary domain:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Frontend engineering (React / Next.js)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Backend engineering (Node.js / Fastify)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mobile engineering (React Native)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;isSelectedEnd&quot;&gt;Working understanding of adjacent disciplines across frontend, backend, mobile, and cloud infrastructure environments&lt;/li&gt;
