&lt;li&gt;Lead cross-functional teams across business, technology, vendors, and operations, aligning contributors to shared outcomes and timelines.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and manage integrated project plans, including milestones, dependencies, risks, and critical path across workstreams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive accountability and ownership, ensuring workstream leads and vendors clearly own delivery not the PM.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively manage risks, issues, and dependencies, escalating early with clear options and recommendations for leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Facilitate effective governance forums (SteerCo, working sessions, exec reviews) with clear agendas, decisions required, and documented outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
